Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:53.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The thoughts that I have looked for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:56.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Are in a lamp on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Drifting slow into~ sunrise morning glow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:14.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She came to me that night for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:18.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I had nothing but my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:22.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And a pocket watch that never would be sold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:33.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"I have all the powers of the moon~ at my feet"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:38.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"To set your mind~ free"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:44.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"The waking light will tell you~ all~ you~ need~~"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:49.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"Oh ba~~by, just sleep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:04.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I went out catching fireflies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:07.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For the stars are more elusive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:11.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And they burn holes in my pockets, don't ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I contemplated my demise~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And she looked at me and smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:33.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Singing, "Where, then, do you think~ you will go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:44.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"The swirl of our eternity has secrets for me~~"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:49.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"And you, as well, to learn its majesty"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:55.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"I'm tired, too, to lift all the light~ you see~~"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:03:02.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"But it's warm in its comfort, and it's brighter in its mystery"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:37.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:48.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:59.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreamed~